1
00:00:58,440 --> 00:01:00,100
I found some clues about Zixi.

2
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,160
I need you to help me restore them.

3
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:02,560
Okay.

4
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,890
Then send them to me.

5
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:04,360
Okay.

6
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,960
I'll bring them to you in a bit.

7
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,360
I'll wait for you at home.

8
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:07,880
Bye.

9
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:20,920
Sir.

10
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:23,280
Luo Xin.

11
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,960
Sorry to disturb you.

12
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,760
Luo Xin.

13
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,880
You're doing this again.

14
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:29,740
You almost gave me a heart attack.

15
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:30,360
Sorry.

16
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:35,020
About what I just said,

17
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,759
did you hear everything?

18
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,360
About your privacy, sir,

19
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,360
as your assistant,

20
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,490
I shouldn't and wouldn't ask too much.

21
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:42,800
Good.

22
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,580
That's professionalism.

23
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,060
Tell me.

24
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,479
What brings you here so suddenly?

25
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,039
The TG new energy vehicles

26
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,759
developed and marketed by Master Haoran

27
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,680
have recently had multiple spontaneous combustion incidents.

28
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,400
The dealers have already gone to the group

29
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,600
to demand compensation.

30
00:01:56,600 --> 00:02:00,000
The chairman asked you to return immediately to deal with it.

31
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,560
This is the information on the new energy vehicles.

32
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,560
Have a quick look.

33
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,440
TG New Energy Vehicles.

34
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,720
Recently,

35
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,520
an accident occurred during the development

36
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,520
of the TG New Energy Racing Project.

37
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:19,680
Chief designer Song Haoming resigned to take responsibility,

38
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,200
and the project is put on hold again.

39
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,200
I just feel like this whole thing...

40
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:32,840
Zixi.

41
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,570
I finally have a clue about you.

42
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,480
Hurry up and compensate us.

43
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,120
Everyone, please quiet down.

44
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:42,920
Compensate us!

45
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:44,000
Please be quiet.

46
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,560
Quiet.

47
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:46,100
We will solve the problem.

48
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,050
I'm telling you,

49
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,720
if you don't give us an explanation today,

50
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,240
I will stop selling Gu's company cars

51
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:50,900
from now on.

52
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:51,880
That's right.

53
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,000
Everyone, calm down.

54
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,600
We are working on a solution.

55
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,480
We're working on it.

56
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,880
Work on what?

57
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,800
In just two months,

58
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,720
out of a hundred TG New Energy Vehicles,

59
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,360
five have spontaneously combusted.

60
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,240
Do you know what the media is saying about us?

61
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,840
That we took your dirty money

62
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,840
to sell fake products.

63
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,320
Yeah.

64
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,250
I'm telling you,

65
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,120
this is already a huge deal.

66
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,880
Not only do we want to return the goods,

67
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,560
but we also want compensation.

68
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,400
Right. Pay up. Pay up.

69
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:14,960
Quiet, everyone.

70
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,760
Pay up.

71
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,200
Quiet.

72
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,600
Pay up. Pay up. Pay up.

73
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,240
We will solve the problem, okay?

74
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,520
Please be quiet first.

75
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,840
There's a good show to watch.

76
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,370
So many people are waiting.

77
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,840
It's just about compensation, right?

78
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,360
Mr. Gu.

79
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,680
It's negotiable.

80
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,360
Mr. Gu.

81
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,360
You're here.

82
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,280
How should we resolve this?

83
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,040
Yes, Mr. Gu.

84
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,840
With so many of us here today,

85
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,600
you must give us an explanation.

86
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,400
You can't expect us to pay for it.

87
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,400
That's right.

88
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,640
All right.

89
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,280
Everyone,

90
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,560
All the TG new energy vehicles you own,

91
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,240
will be recalled by the Gu Group.

92
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:45,920
Within three days,

93
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,200
we will find out the truth

94
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,640
and give everyone an answer.

95
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:50,200
If there is indeed a quality issue,

96
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,040
the Gu Group

97
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,440
will compensate double for your losses.

98
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:53,600
Is that okay?

99
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,520
You said it yourself.

100
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,760
Okay, let's do this.

101
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,160
Mr. Gu, you must keep your word.

102
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,760
Everyone,

103
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,400
our Gu Group

104
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:02,410
has always valued its reputation as its life.

105
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,640
Since the president has spoken,

106
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,740
we will definitely do what we say.

107
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,820
Right, Haoran?

108
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,130
Exactly.

109
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,280
However,

110
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,170
do you know according to the contract,

111
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,420
how much the double compensation is?

112
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:27,200
Making the Gu Group pay 500 million

113
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,600
just based on your words,

114
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,240
is simply ridiculous.

115
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,280
Old Mr. Gu,

116
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,930
I believe the Gu Group's success today

117
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,480
relies not only on money,

118
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,680
but more on integrity and character.

119
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,680
Old Mr. Gu, you...

120
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,840
Please give me time and authority.

121
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,370
I believe I can handle this.

122
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:50,040
Do you think you're playing Monopoly?

123
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,760
What if you can't?

124
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,600
Then you can do whatever you want with me.

125
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,240
Okay.

126
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:55,760
If you fail,

127
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,860
I will cripple both your arms.

128
00:04:59,360 --> 00:04:59,960
What?

129
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,080
Arms are a racer's life.

130
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,680
Too scared to bet?

131
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,360
If you're scared,

132
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,600
just admit your mistake

133
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:14,200
and let Haotian handle this.

134
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,440
For Zixi,

135
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:17,920
I have to go.

136
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,400
Okay.

137
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:22,880
It's a deal.

138
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,400
I will give you

139
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:30,040
full authority over the Gu Group right now.

140
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,280
In three days,

141
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,240
I want to see the results.

142
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,320
Thank you, Mr. Gu.

143
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,720
Chairman,

144
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,280
are you just going to let him do whatever he wants?

145
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,360
I don't know why,

146
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,200
but I see

147
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,080
my younger self in him.

148
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:59,760
You are not allowed to interfere in this matter.

149
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,800
I want to see

150
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:03,410
what this waiter from the karaoke hall

151
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,200
is capable of.

152
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:07,840
Yes.

153
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,640
Highest access granted.

154
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,720
There is a deleted file here.

155
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,200
Captain.

156
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,000
Not that fast.

157
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,680
The voice recorder is still being repaired.

158
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,120
Help me restore a document first.

159
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,250
This is more urgent.

160
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:36,880
Okay.

161
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,770
Alright.

162
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,760
Li Group

163
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,970
has been kicked off the supplier list.

164
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:12,640
Why is Gu Group still using their steel plates?

165
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,480
Maybe

166
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,420
the problem lies here.

167
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,080
6-40mm: length.

168
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,320
Length: 4500mm;

169
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,180
Width: 1500mm;

170
00:07:57,680 --> 00:08:00,540
The die-casting thickness is indeed substandard.

171
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:17,320
Gu Group knows the die-casting thickness is substandard.

172
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,520
But why do they still cooperate with them?

173
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,120
Could it be

174
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,330
that the problem lies here?

175
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,659
Who are you?

176
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,480
What are you doing?

177
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,440
I...

178
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,039
Don't run.

179
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,039
Thief.

180
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,880
Stop!

181
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,080
Stop!

182
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,120
Stop!

183
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,200
Don't run!

184
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,160
Catch the thief!

185
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,610
Catch the thief!

186
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,280
Young Master.

187
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:47,680
Luo Xin,

188
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,480
get in the car!

189
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,600
Stop!

190
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:52,280
Stop!

191
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,320
Catch the thief!
